Package utilities

Class MonthAndTypeData

java.lang.Object
utilities.MonthAndTypeData
public class MonthAndTypeData extends Object
This is the MonthAndTypeData class which is used to gather appointment data for the AppointmentsByMonthAndType screen. The data gathered is the month the appointment occurred, the type of appointment, and the number of those appointments.
